<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250074>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1 – 4. Feeding behavior of adult Cetoniinae: Fig. 1, Allorhina sp., Gymnetis carbo and G. g o r y i feeding on sap of undetermined tree (Pitanguí, Minas Gerais, Brazil, photograph by Nicodemos Rosa); Fig. 2, Gymnetis bonplandi feeding on sap of undetermined tree (Pitanguí, Minas Gerais, Brazil, photograph by Nicodemos Rosa); Fig. 3, Gymnetis strigosa on flowers of Marsdenia woodburiana [Asclepiadaceae] (photograph by Alex Segarra, 17 May 2013); Fig. 4, Gymnetis hepatica, feeding on sap of Sphaeralcea bonariensis, together with Euphoria lurida (Sachayoj, Santiago del Estero, Argentina)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/250074/files/figure.png" .
